{{short description|A seamount in the Southern Ocean}}
'''Lichtner Seamount''' ({{coord|67|33|S|0|40|W|source:GNIS|display=inline,title}}) is a seamount located in the [[Southern Ocean]]. The name, for German cartographer [[Werner Lichtner]], was approved by the [[Advisory Committee for Undersea Features]] in April 2000.<ref name=gnis/>

